{"tid":687174,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過收唔到電話","createTime":"2018-06-02T04:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T05:04:17.000Z","uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1a5e0d16fbdf64a8ebfbaaf289abad021b3e9e","tid":687174,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:12:42.000Z","msg":"呢個星期發生過兩次<br />\n出面打入黎，明明個電話無熄，網絡覆蓋到嘅地方，但個電話無響過<br />\n<br />\n一次係老媽子打黎，跟住我check返，真係有打過畀我但我無響過<br />\n<br />\n一次係無端端收到個留言，咁正常係打唔到畀我先有留言架嘛，但收到留言之前個段時間個電話都無響過<br />\n<br />\n利伸用緊3台sony<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf83c13e9156d0d6443c6139029920c9c0846c03","tid":687174,"uid":179571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00cc027e00819a169796d23bc0045f3ea3407bc5","tid":687174,"uid":14788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"我長期都收唔到電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ee04a10a4728bbff72a1d12cfd9df057a70115","tid":687174,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00cc027e00819a169796d23bc0045f3ea3407bc5","tid":687174,"uid":14788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"我長期都收唔到電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"正常既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798fa557b1513171ec6450aebda7f4871ad4c3ec","tid":687174,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00cc027e00819a169796d23bc0045f3ea3407bc5","tid":687174,"uid":14788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"我長期都收唔到電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/130416_0168375b326155a4f8ea4e2